The "For My Family" License

This software is free to use, share, and modify — as long as you're doing something good with it.

No warranties, no guarantees, no lawyers. If it breaks, fix it and share the fix.

Dedicated to my family, who deserves to understand the world in their own language — especially
the little one who can't read subtitles fast enough yet.

免責聲明：本軟體無法保證翻譯品質，但至少比我爸的英文好。
(Disclaimer: translation quality not guaranteed, but at least it's better than my dad's English.)
